&lt;p&gt;***** Previous applicants need not apply. ******&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a dynamic Staff Nurse to join our District Nursing Service to deliver a high quality nursing care to the vibrant and diverse residents of Brent. We provide care as part of planned packages as well as respond to unscheduled call outs to meet the needs of a wide variety of patients.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;If you are caring, innovative, motivated, forward thinking and you see community nursing as your career option, then this could be the job for you.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We are looking for a dedicated and knowledgeable Registered Nurse, who is able to provide high standards of care to our patients. The post holder must have effective communication skills, must be prepared to gain extended skills and work collaboratively to meet the needs of the service. The post holder will be expected to be able to travel independently across the borough.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Brent community services are flexible and can offer long days to candidates if it suits them.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameKindy KaurAdditional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kindy Kaur via email on kindykaur@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
